### PUT request to update a person
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/people
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "2",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doechii",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-01",
  "timeOfRegistration": "2023-10-10T14:30:00Z",
  "addressLocation": {
    "latitude": 50.8503,
    "longitude": 4.3517
  },
  "behavior": "nice",
  "version": 1
}

### GET request to fetch all people
GET http://localhost:8000/api/people
Accept: application/json

